A Chaunceller. 30 Gentlemen of the Artillerie, which do attend vpon the person of the Generall of the Ordinance. 30 Hargulutiers or hargubuze on horsebacke, attending also vpon him: 8 Halbardiers for his guard: two or three Interpreters attending vpon his person;
                        Other people belonging to the Commaunder.
                      a Minister or Preacher, a Phisition, a maister Chirurgian and his seruant, a Trumpeter, two or three Enginers or more, two or three Refiners of powder, or as neede shall require.

